name: Tesla Model S
description: The Tesla Model S is a full-size electric luxury sedan that redefines what an electric vehicle can be. With its sleek design, cutting-edge technology, and impressive performance, it represents the future of automotive engineering.

name: BMW M3
description: The BMW M3 is the ultimate expression of BMW's motorsport heritage in a road-going sedan. With its high-revving inline-six engine, precise handling, and aggressive styling, it delivers an exhilarating driving experience that few cars can match.

name: Mercedes AMG GT
description: The Mercedes-AMG GT represents the pinnacle of Mercedes-Benz performance and luxury. With its handcrafted AMG V8 engine, stunning design, and cutting-edge technology, it delivers an unforgettable driving experience that combines power with elegance.

name: Audi R8
description: The Audi R8 is a mid-engine supercar that brings Formula 1 technology to the road. With its naturally aspirated V10 engine, quattro all-wheel drive, and striking design, it delivers an exhilarating driving experience that combines performance with everyday usability.

name: Porsche 911
description: The Porsche 911 is an automotive icon that has defined the sports car segment for over five decades. With its rear-engine layout, timeless design, and exceptional driving dynamics, it represents the perfect balance of performance, comfort, and everyday usability.
